title: International Plaza to host Latin American and Caribbean-themed Father’s Day celebration Sunday
description: The International Plaza, 828 N. Clinton Ave., will host a special Latin American- and Caribbean-themed Father’s Day celebration at 1 p.m. Sunday, June 15 featuring live entertainment, music, and community games to honor the role fathers and father figures play in our community.The day’s lineup includes a performance by Mairy, along with music provided by DJ Franco. Guests can also join in friendly games of dominos, a favorite family pastime in many Latin American and Caribbean nations and communities.
